      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know i should check but my sensor is acting weird and i dont have my glucometer on me right now. honestly i feel terrible and just want this to stop. if i take like 5 units of my fast acting insulin it should probably help balance things out since i feel so off, right? it feels like i'm spiking from the run.",
